# Meeting API

## Schedule Meeting

Creates a new meeting request.

### Endpoint

```
POST /api/meetings
```

### Authentication

Required

### Request Body

```json
{
  "title":"Investment Discussion",
  "description":"Discuss funding opportunity",
  "meetingType":"Video Call",
  "date":"2026-07-20",
  "startTime":"15:00",
  "endTime":"16:00",
  "investor":"USER_ID"
}
```

### Success Response

```json
{
    "success": true,
    "message":"Meeting scheduled successfully."
}
```

### Possible Responses

| Status | Description           |
| ------ | --------------------- |
| 201    | Meeting created       |
| 400    | Missing fields        |
| 409    | Meeting time conflict |
| 500    | Server error          |

### Features

* Creates meeting requests.
* Prevents scheduling conflicts.
* Supports Video, Phone and In Person meetings.
* Stores meeting creator.
* Default status is Pending.

---

## Get My Meetings

### Endpoint

```
GET /api/meetings
```

### Authentication

Required

### Features

* Returns all meetings.
* Populates investor and entrepreneur information.
* Sorts meetings by status and date.
