---

## Get Single Meeting

### Endpoint

```
GET /api/meetings/:id
```

### Features

* Returns complete meeting information.
* Populates participant details.

---

## Accept Meeting

### Endpoint

```
PUT /api/meetings/:id/accept
```

### Features

* Changes status to Accepted.
* Only intended participant can accept.
* Saves updated meeting.

---

## Reject Meeting

### Endpoint

```
PUT /api/meetings/:id/reject
```

### Features

* Changes status to Rejected.
* Prevents unauthorized access.

---

## Cancel Meeting

### Endpoint

```
PUT /api/meetings/:id/cancel
```

### Features

* Cancels scheduled meeting.
* Updates meeting status.

---

## Delete Meeting

### Endpoint

```
DELETE /api/meetings/:id
```

### Features

* Deletes meeting.
* Only authorized users may delete.
* Removes meeting from database.

