# Document API

## Upload Document

Uploads a PDF document.

### Endpoint

```
POST /api/documents/upload
```

### Authentication

Required

### Content-Type

```
multipart/form-data
```

### Form Data

| Key      | Type |
| -------- | ---- |
| title    | Text |
| document | File |

### Features

* Uploads PDF document.
* Stores metadata.
* Generates document version.
* Stores uploadedBy.
* Creates downloadable file URL.

---

## Get My Documents

### Endpoint

```
GET /api/documents
```

### Authentication

Required

### Features

* Returns authenticated user's documents.
* Sorted by upload date.
* Includes file URL.

---

## Get Single Document

### Endpoint

```
GET /api/documents/:id
```

### Features

* Returns document metadata.
* Includes uploader information.
* Generates preview URL.

---

## Download Document

### Endpoint

```
GET /api/documents/download/:id
```

### Features

* Downloads original uploaded PDF.
* Preserves original filename.
* Checks file existence.

---

## Delete Document

### Endpoint

```
DELETE /api/documents/:id
```

### Features

* Deletes uploaded document.
* Removes physical PDF from uploads folder.
* Only uploader can delete.

---

## Sign Document

### Endpoint

```
PUT /api/documents/sign/:id
```

### Authentication

Required

### Request Body

```json
{
   "signature":"data:image/png;base64,..."
}
```

### Features

* Saves handwritten digital signature.
* Stores signature image.
* Updates status to Signed.
* Prevents unauthorized signing.

